/bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/find-your-dream-home.png" alt="Find Your Dream Home" width="381" height="593" />[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="our-lifestyle"]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="3/5"]\r\n<h2>Our Lifestyle</h2>\r\nWith more than 3,000 acres dedicated to lakes, trails and parks, Bridgeland seamlessly blends nature into residents'' daily lives. Our community offers an unrivaled balance: the tranquility of a seemingly untouched natural environment and the convenience of modern facilities and amenities.\r\n\r\nThe community was designed to conserve and enhance the natural environment, with existing lakes and creeks incorporated into the plan as unique amenities. Parks and green space can be found no more than a quarter mile from each homesite and are connected through the community''s vast trail system. Other amenities include a resort-style pool, a disc-golf course, stocked lakes and complimentary use of kayaks, paddle boats and other recreational equipment. Eventually, a 900-acre Town Center will host upscale retail and dining venues while four smaller village center will offer quick access to everyday conveniences.\r\n\r\n[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[su_column size="2/5"]<img class="alignnone wp-image-50 size-full" src="http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/premiere_community.png" alt="premiere_community" width="360" height="254" />[/su_column]\r\n\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="video"]\r\n[su_column size="1/1"]<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2hBAPrwYINo?rel=0&amp;controls=0&amp;showinfo=0" width="560" height="315" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>[/su_column]\r\n[/su_row]\r\n\r\n[su_row class="google-map"]\r\n[su_column size="1/1"]\r\n<div class="overlay"></div>\r\n<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d13828.142527003609!2d-95.73529244999996!3d29.949653700000006!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x86412a06400268f9%3A0x2cdbdea23e7194c!2sBridgeland%2C+Cypress%2C+TX+77433!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1442344675414" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>[/su_column]\r\n[/su_row]', 'Homepage', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-15 19:18:26', '2015-09-15 19:18:26', '', 4, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
