(142, 1, '2015-09-16 16:34:33', '2015-09-16 16:34:33', 'Bridgeland provides numerous opportunities throughout the year to enjoy the unique features the community has to offer.  With trails, boating, swimming, disc golf and events like concerts in the park, there are lots of reasons to get outside and play!\r\n\r\nThe event calendar offers a variety of public events, instructional classes such as kayaking and fishing and much more to provide a taste of what life is like in Bridgeland.\r\n\r\nSign up to receive invitations to events and receive community updates as Bridgeland grows.  To see how much fun our residents are having, visit <a href="http://www.bridgelandlife.com/">www.bridgelandlife.com</a>.', 'Events', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'events', '', '', '2015-09-22 20:47:24', '2015-09-22 20:47:24', '', 138, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/?page_id=142', 1, 'page', '', 0),
