(214, 1, '2015-09-29 13:53:51', '2015-09-29 13:53:51', '<h3><em>A plan for all seasons</em></h3>\nBridgeland does not take the label “<strong>master planned community</strong>” lightly. In fact, developers created a road map for the evolution of Bridgeland very early in the community’s history. This blueprint is a multi-layered approach for the placement of residential neighborhoods, a hierarchy of parks and amenities, as well as public and private schools. Additionally, a detailed preservation plan outlines the community’s environmentally conscious approaches to irrigation, energy and wildlife.\n\n[su_tabs vertical="yes"]\n\n[su_tab title="Master Environmental Plan"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/su_tab]\n\n[su_tab title="Master Parks Plan"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/su_tab]\n\n[su_tab title="Master Education Plan"]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/su_tab]\n\n[/su_tabs]\n<p dir="ltr"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-217" src="http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/mallard-Lake-2.jpg" alt="mallard Lake 2" width="1024" height="683" /></p>', 'Thoughtfully Planned', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '106-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-29 13:53:51', '2015-09-29 13:53:51', '', 106, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/106-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
