(233, 1, '2015-09-21 14:34:01', '2015-09-21 14:34:01', 'Bridgeland is managed by The Woodlands Development Company (TWDC). As the developer of the best-selling community in Houston since 1990, TWDC brings 40 years of successful real estate experience.\n\nThe <a href="http://www.howardhughes.com/" target="_blank">Howard Hughes Corporation</a>, which is the parent company of TWDC, develops commercial, residential and mixed-use real estate throughout the United States, including Las Vegas, Manhattan and Honolulu. As owner of Bridgeland and The Woodlands, the Howard Hughes Corporation is one of the largest master planned community developers in the Houston area.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Your Developer', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '108-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-21 14:34:01', '2015-09-21 14:34:01', '', 108, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/108-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
