(278, 1, '2015-09-21 15:33:54', '2015-09-21 15:33:54', 'Connectivity and convenience play an important role in the planning of Bridgeland. There will be four distinct villages within the community, defining the land plan and offering residents easy walking and biking access to parks and trails, playgrounds, pool complexes, schools, employment, worship and shopping.\r\n\r\nEach village offers a wide range of housing prices, styles and densities, from conventional neighborhoods to custom home designs in excess of $1 million. Lakeland Village is the first of four villages to open in Bridgeland, to be followed by Parkland Village, Prairieland Village and Creekland Village as development continues.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-277" src="http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/LLH_1.jpg" alt="LLH_1" width="1024" height="683" />', 'Village Life', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '127-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-21 15:33:54', '2015-09-21 15:33:54', '', 127, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/127-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(279, 1, '2015-09-21 15:34:39', '2015-09-21 15:34:39', '<h3><em>Cradle to Career and Beyond</em></h3>\r\nBridgeland has developed a Master Education Plan that includes pre-school, special-needs, private and public school sites. Additionally, Bridgeland hopes to have satellite locations and/or a University Center close to its Town Center, as well as easy access to continuing education courses.\r\n\r\nThree highly-acclaimed public school districts will eventually service Bridgeland: <a href="http://www.cfisd.net/en/" target="_blank">Cypress-Fairbanks Independent School District</a>,<a href="http://www.katyisd.org/" target="_blank"> Katy Independent School District</a> and <a href="http://www.wallerisd.net/" target="_blank">Waller Independent School District</a>.\r\n\r\nCurrently, students living in Bridgeland attend Cy-Fair ISD''s <a href="http://pope.cfisd.net/en/" target="_blank">Pope Elementary</a>, <a href="http://smith.cfisd.net/en/" target="_blank">Smith Middle</a> or <a href="http://cyranch.cfisd.net/en/">Cy-Ranch High</a>.  Smith and Cy-Ranch are located directly across the street from Bridgeland’s main entry.  Even closer, Pope Elementary is nestled within The Cove.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.nces.ed.gov/ccd/districtsearch/district_detail.asp?Search=2&amp;DistrictID=4816110&amp;ID2=4816110&amp;details=" target="_blank">Download Cy-Fair ISD''s report card</a>\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iTZ9FBjLoFE', 'Education', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '129-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-21 15:34:39', '2015-09-21 15:34:39', '', 129, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/129-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
