(346, 1, '2015-09-22 17:46:37', '2015-09-22 17:46:37', 'The Oak Meadow Open on September 26th is a PDGA sanctioned disc golf tournament. Players from Bridgeland and all over Texas will compete in professional and amateur divisions for both men and women. All players will receive a custom Bridgeland putter from Gateway discs. There will be an in round closest to the pin contest and ring of fire event after the tournament for a chance to win more prizes. Check in begins at 7:30 and we will have a player meeting at 8:30. The event is 2 rounds of 18 holes. Register online at dgscene.com/oakmeadowopen.', 'Oak Meadow Park Open', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '344-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-22 17:46:37', '2015-09-22 17:46:37', '', 344, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/344-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(347, 1, '2015-09-22 17:47:32', '2015-09-22 17:47:32', 'Bridgeland provides numerous opportunities throughout the year to enjoy the unique features the community has to offer.  With trails, boating, swimming, disc golf and events like concerts in the park, there are lots of reasons to get outside and play!\r\n\r\nThe event calendar offers a variety of public events, instructional classes such as kayaking and fishing and much more to provide a taste of what life is like in Bridgeland.\r\n\r\nSign up to receive invitations to events and receive community updates as Bridgeland grows.  To see how much fun our residents are having, visit <a href="http://www.bridgelandlife.com/">www.bridgelandlife.com</a>.\r\n\r\n[ecwd id="344"]', 'Events', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '142-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-22 17:47:32', '2015-09-22 17:47:32', '', 142, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/142-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(348, 1, '2015-09-22 17:51:36', '2015-09-22 17:51:36', '<h3>Disc Golf Tournament</h3>\r\nThe Oak Meadow Open on September 26th is a PDGA sanctioned disc golf tournament. Players from Bridgeland and all over Texas will compete in professional and amateur divisions for both men and women. All players will receive a custom Bridgeland putter from Gateway discs. There will be an in round closest to the pin contest and ring of fire event after the tournament for a chance to win more prizes. Check in begins at 7:30 and we will have a player meeting at 8:30. The event is 2 rounds of 18 holes. Register online at <a href="http://dgscene.com/oakmeadowopen" target="_blank">dgscene.com/oakmeadowopen</a>.', 'Oak Meadow Park Open', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'oak-meadow-park-open', '', '', '2015-09-22 19:38:05', '2015-09-22 19:38:05', '', 0, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/?post_type=ecwd_event&#038;p=348', 0, 'ecwd_event', '', 0);
