petitive sporting events throughout the year.\r\n\r\n“It’s an honor to have the Cypress Triathlon within Bridgeland each year,” said Lona Shipp, Marketing Director for Bridgeland. “Our neighborhood is filled with running trails, biking paths and large lakes, making it an ideal location for a triathlon.”\r\n\r\nTo register or to volunteer to help throughout the weekend, visit <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/">www.bridgeland.com</a>.', 'The Cypress Triathlon Planned for Weekend of July 25th in Bridgeland', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '384-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-24 13:17:11', '2015-09-24 13:17:11', '', 384, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/384-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
