(395, 1, '2015-06-08 13:37:19', '2015-06-08 13:37:19', 'The Farmers Market at <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/">Bridgeland</a> will feature an assembly of home-grown grocers and gardeners Sunday, June 14 from 12:30-3:30 p.m., as well as an orchid-growing class led by Bruce Cameron of Orchid Obsession, a local grower, wholesaler and retailer of the plant.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<div class="media media-element-container media-default"><img class="media-element file-default alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/BridgelandOrchid.jpg" alt="" width="298" height="416" /></div>\r\nCameron, owner of the Spring-based business, says his complimentary class at 1 p.m. will teach attendees about the different varieties of orchids and how to properly care for the plant.\r\n\r\n“I’ll be covering watering, fertilizing, lighting, when and how to repot and what to watch out for when purchasing,” Cameron said. “I also encourage people to bring ailing orchids to the class so I can diagnose the problem and make a decision about whether or not the plant can be saved.”\r\n\r\nMarket goers will also find a plethora of peak-season produce, including okra, kale, zucchini, dewberries, cucumbers, radishes and a variety of peppers. Additional offerings include an assortment of organic meats, free-range eggs, homemade pastas and fresh cheeses.\r\n\r\nOther vendors will sell natural products like paraben-free soaps, non-toxic cleaning supplies, olive-oil based lotions and Texas lavender soy candles.\r\n\r\nHeld on the second Sunday of every month near Bridgeland’s Lakeland Activity Center, 16902 Bridgeland Landing, The Farmers Market at Bridgeland unites community farmers, growers and producers with area residents. To see a full list of this month’s participating vendors, visit <a href="http://www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org/">www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org.</a>', 'Vendor at Bridgeland Farmers Marker to Offer Orchid Growing Class June 14', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vendor-at-bridgeland-farmers-marker-to-offer-orchid-growing-class-june-14', '', '', '2015-09-24 13:38:06', '2015-09-24 13:38:06', '', 0, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/?p=395', 0, 'post', '', 0),
