(397, 1, '2015-05-20 13:39:26', '2015-05-20 13:39:26', 'With the school year winding down, Bridgeland’s full-time Activities Director is preparing to host a variety of summer day camps for both resident and local youth.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nStarting in June, children ages 3 and up can participate in camps taking place mornings and afternoons throughout the summer at the Lakeland Activity Center, 16902 Bridgeland Landing.\r\n\r\n<strong>Art Exploration Camp</strong>\r\n\r\nThis camp will focus on the creative process. Children will have the opportunity to explore different art techniques and materials.  They will also get to create 2D and 3D art.  Each week will offer a different set of projects.\r\n<table border="0" width="786" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Session</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Registration</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Fees</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Info</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Register</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>June 22-25</td>\r\n<td>Closes Jun 19th</td>\r\n<td>$80.00/$90.00</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/"><strong><u> Info</u></strong></a></td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/#register"><strong><u> Register</u></strong></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>July 6-9</td>\r\n<td>Closes Jul 3rd</td>\r\n<td>$80.00/$90.00</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/"><strong><u> Info</u></strong></a></td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/#register"><strong><u> Register</u></strong></a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>August 3-6</td>\r\n<td>Closes Jul 31st</td>\r\n<td>$80.00/$90.00</td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/"><strong><u> Info</u></strong></a></td>\r\n<td><a href="https://secure.rec1.com/TX/Bridgeland-Community-Associations/#register"><strong><u> Register</u></strong></a>