(406, 1, '2015-05-20 16:51:46', '2015-05-20 16:51:46', 'To showcase Bridgeland’s new neighborhoods and models, the community has introduced the Master of Real Estate Program, an incentive package for agents who sell a home in the community on or before June 15<sup>th</sup>.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n<div class="media media-element-container media-default"><img class="media-element file-default alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/Bridgeland_MastersOfRealEstateProgram_April%202015_FINAL_0.jpg" alt="" width="378" height="302" /></div>\r\nFor every home sold, agents will not only be given a $500 gift card, but also a chance to win grand prizes valued at $3,000, $2,000 or $1,000. Additionally, when a Realtor registers a client at Bridgeland’s Welcome Center, he or she will be given a $25 lunch voucher.\r\n\r\nWith a range of styles in Lakeland Heights and Hidden Creek, buyers are sure to find a variety of homes in Bridgeland that fit their various tastes and specific needs.\r\n\r\nHidden Creek will host 1,000 home sites, a 20-acre park, 142 acres of lakes and homes built by <a href="http://www.beazer.com/houston-TX/bridgeland-hidden-creek---55" target="_blank"><u>Beazer Homes</u></a>, <a href="http://www.coventryhomes.com/"><u>Coventry Homes</u></a>, <a href="http://www.darlinghomes.com/new-homes/texas/houston/cypress/bridgeland-hidden-creek-community" target="_blank"><u>Darling Homes</u></a>, <a href="http://www.meritagehomes.com/search/houston-tx/bridgeland-hidden-creek/" target="_blank"><u>Meritage Homes</u></a>, <a href="http://www.perryhomes.com/find-your-home/houston/bridgeland.aspx" target="_blank"><u>Perry Homes</u></a>, <a href="http://www.ryland.com/find-your-new-home/11-houston/6311-bridgeland.html" target="_blank"><u>Ryland Homes</u></a>, <a href="http://www.taylormorrison.com/new-homes/texas/houston/cypress/bridgeland-community" target="_blank"><u>Taylor Morrison Homes</u></a>, <a href="http://www.lennar.com/New-Homes/Texas/Houston/Cypress/Bridgeland/Classic-and-Wentworth-Collections" target="_blank"><u>Village Builders</u></a> and <a href="http://westin-homes.com/communities/details/6065" target="_blank"><u>Westin Homes</u></a>. Homes in this area start at $300,000 and can exceed $1 million.\r\n\r\nLakeland Heights'' price range is from the $250s to $400s. Homes are built by <a href="http://www.davidweekleyhomes.com/new-homes/tx/houston/cypress/lakeland-heights-50" target="_blank"><u>David Weekley Homes</u></a>, <a href="http://www.jkylehomes.com/lakeland-heights-bridgeland/" target="_blank"><u>J. Kyle Homes</u></a>and <a href="http://www.perryhomes.com/Find-Your-Home/Houston/Bridgeland/Bridgeland---Townhomes-of-Lakeland-Heights" target="_blank"><u>Perry Homes</u></a>. The community also provides walking-distance access to local schools, Lakeland Activity Center and the future Lakeland Village Center.\r\n\r\nFor more information, please contact Bridgeland’s Welcome Center at 281-304-5588.', 'Masters of Real Estate Program', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'masters-of-real-estate-program', '', '', '2015-09-24 16:53:04', '2015-09-24 16:53:04', '', 0, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/?p=406', 0, 'post', '', 0);
