(443, 1, '2014-12-08 18:16:49', '2014-12-08 18:16:49', '<div class="field field-name-post-date field-type-ds field-label-hidden field-wrapper">\r\n<p class="subheader">The Farmers Market at Bridgeland, set for 12:30 – 3:30 p.m. Sunday, Dec. 14, is sure to impress both grocery and gift shoppers with an assortment of seasonal crops and locally-handcrafted goods.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="body field">\r\n\r\n<span class="caption none media-image alignright size-medium wp-image-2444"><a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/files/novembermarket-300x19810jpg"><img src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/NovemberMarket-300x198_10.jpg?itok=mplkNHOd" alt="November Market" width="220" height="145" /></a></span>\r\n\r\nSince May of 2012, thoughtful consumers from throughout the Cypress area have attended the gathering at Lakeland Activity Center, 16902 Bridgeland Landing, on the second Sunday of every month. The market hosts vendors that sell wholesome, season-ready produce, free-range eggs and a plethora of unique, homemade products. In addition to the ordinary lineup, however, the December assembly is part of a two-month ‘Artisan Market Days’ theme, which spotlights merchandise from local painters, sculptors, jewelry makers and others artists – just in time for the holiday season.\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n\r\n“The volunteers that organize The Farmers Market at Bridgeland work so hard to put on a great event,” said Martha Gros, Bridgeland’s marketing coordinator. “The artists they’re bringing in are very talented and we think shoppers will really enjoy perusing the products and finding holiday gifts for loved ones.”\r\n\r\nTo see a full list of this month’s participating vendors, visit <a href="http://www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org/">www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org</a>.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'The Farmers Market at Bridgeland Offers Produce and Presents', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-farmers-market-at-bridgeland-offers-produce-and-presents', '', '', '2015-09-24 18:18:09', '2015-09-24 18:18:09', '', 0, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/?p=443', 0, 'post', '', 0),
