(445, 1, '2014-12-04 18:27:49', '2014-12-04 18:27:49', 'Bridgeland® announced today that two of its builders, Beazer Homes and Ryland Homes, will open their models on Saturday, December 13th in Hidden Creek, the newest and largest neighborhood to date of the award-winning, 11,400-acre master planned community. The public is invited to tour the new showcase homes, the newest models to be unveiled in Hidden Creek, from 1pm to 3pm at 16711 and 16707 Blooming Plum Drive. Alongside the opportunity to walk the floorplans, guests will be eligible to win various giveaways, offered light refreshments, and in the spirit of the season, have the chance to take photos with Santa.\r\n\r\n<span class="caption none media-image alignright size-full wp-image-2453"><a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/files/cove-model-homes-012jpg"><img class="alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/Cove-Model-Homes-01_2.jpg?itok=HL9j9mO8" alt="Cove Model Homes" width="220" height="147" /></a></span>\r\n\r\n“We’re excited to begin showcasing our builders’ latest models in Hidden Creek,” said Peter Houghton, Vice President of Master Planned Communities for Bridgeland. “These openings come at an exciting time as northwest Houston rapidly expands, and Bridgeland continues to attract buyers with its wide range of desirable housing, resort-style amenities and top-notch schools.”\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nBeazer’s new homes in Hidden Creek range from 2,140 to 2,998 square feet and are priced from the low $300s. As an ENERGY STAR® Partner of the Year, Beazer builds its homes to be 100% Energy Star 3.0, meaning lower utility bills for homeowners. Plus, all floorplans offer free ‘choice options.’ allowing buyers the flexibility to personalize their homes at no additional cost.\r\n\r\nRyland is offering five different floorplans in Hidden Creek that vary from 2,023 to 2,499 square feet and start in the low $300s. With Ryland’s signature HouseWorks® program, new homes are designed to preserve the environment, conserve energy and provide more comfort while also reducing the price of monthly utilities.\r\n\r\nIn addition to Beazer and Ryland, Darling Homes, Meritage Homes, Perry Homes, Taylor Morrison Homes, Village Builders and Westin Homes are also building in Hidden Creek, which features 1,000 homesites priced from the low $300s to over $1 million.\r\n\r\nHidden Creek will introduce an extensive array of amenities, including Lakeland Village Park, a 20-acre green space that will feature a fenced dog park, basketball court, canoe launch and skate park. Additional tennis courts, picnic areas, walking trails and pavilions also are planned as well as a new splash pad, playground and heated lap pool, which will be open year-round. Josey Lake, an expansive waterway that runs along the perimeter of Hidden Creek, will enable residents to canoe three miles from end to end or stop and explore the birding tower and boardwalk along the way.\r\n\r\nAlong with Lakeland Village Park, Hidden Creek also will have three smaller multi-use green spaces, including Tree House Park, which will enable children to play and explore among some of the live oaks that date back to the property’s early rice farming days. Similar to other sections of Lakeland Village, an extensive trail system will be nestled within Hidden Creek, including a 12-foot-wide hike-and-bike trail that will follow along Bridgeland Creek Parkway and Josey Ranch Road. The trail will eventually lead directly to Bridgeland’s Town Center, where the community’s dining, shopping, entertainment and employment venues will be located.\r\n\r\nBridgeland won the 2013 “Master Planned Development of the Year” award from the Greater Houston Builders Association (GHBA), just one of the more than 100 accolades the community has received. For more information on Bridgeland or its builders’ models, visit <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/">www.bridgeland.com</a>, Facebook or Twitter.', 'Beazer Homes and Ryland Homes Co-host Grand Opening of Models in Hidden Creek on December 13', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'beazer-homes-and-ryland-homes-co-host-grand-opening-of-models-in-hidden-creek-on-december-13', '', '', '2015-09-24 18:54:52', '2015-09-24 18:54:52', '', 0, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/?p=445', 0, 'post', '', 0),
