(460, 1, '2014-10-02 19:02:23', '2014-10-02 19:02:23', 'Perry Homes has opened a 4,449-square-foot model in Hidden Creek, the newest neighborhood in the award-winning, 11,400-acre master planned community.<span class="caption none media-image alignright size-medium wp-image-2424"><a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/files/4499w-1-lo-res-300x1974jpg"><img class="alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/4499W-1-lo-res-300x197_4.jpg?itok=1Y4djFLA" alt="4499W 1 lo-res" width="220" height="144" /></a></span>\r\n\r\nThe showcase home, which is located on 17222 Heron Crest Drive, features five bedrooms, four-and-a-half bathrooms, a media room, a formal dining room, a library and a number of Perry’s signature details like eight-foot doors throughout the house, granite bathroom countertops and upgraded kitchen amenities.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nAs you enter the home, the entry-way is framed by a formal dining room, living room and curved staircase. The open-concept family room has an 18-foot ceiling featuring a fireplace and wall of windows. The family room flows into the kitchen that features an island with built-in seating space and a walk-in pantry that has easy access to the formal dining room. The private master suite has a curved wall of windows and an 11-foot tray ceiling. The master bath retreat includes a garden tub, separate glass-enclosed shower, dual vanities, a linen closet and two large walk-in closets. The upstairs features a spacious game room, adjoining media room and secondary bedrooms.\r\n\r\nBeazer Homes, Darling Homes, Meritage Homes, Ryland Homes, Taylor Morrison Homes, Village Builders and Westin Homes will also build alongside Perry Homes in Hidden Creek, the largest section in Bridgeland to date with 1,000 homesites set alongside 142 acres of lakes and waterways. New luxury homes are expected to range in price from $280,000 to over $1 million.\r\n\r\n“Hidden Creek will showcase Perry’s top-notch product alongside eight other well-known builders,” said Peter Houghton, Vice President of Master Planned Communities for Bridgeland. “The opening of our largest neighborhood and expansion of Lakeland Heights comes at an exciting time given the tremendous demand for upscale homes in the northwest Houston area. Bridgeland continues to attract buyers with its wide range of desirable housing, resort-style amenities and exemplary schools.”\r\n\r\nIn addition to being the newest and largest community within Lakeland Village, Hidden Creek will introduce an extensive array of amenities, including Lakeland Village Park, a 20-acre green space that will feature an enclosed dog park, basketball court, canoe launch and skate park. Additional tennis courts, picnic areas, walking trails and pavilions also are planned, as well as a new splash pad, playground and heated lap pool, which will be open year-round.\r\n\r\nAlong with Lakeland Village Park, Hidden Creek also will have three smaller multi-use green spaces, including Tree House Park, which will enable children to play and explore among some of the live oaks that date back to the property’s early rice farming days. Similar to other sections of Lakeland Village, an extensive trail system will be nestled within Hidden Creek, including a 12-foot-wide hike-and-bike trail that will follow along Bridgeland Creek Parkway and Josey Ranch Road. The trail will eventually lead directly to Bridgeland’s Town Center, where the community’s dining, shopping, entertainment and employment venues will be located.\r\nJosey Lake, an 140-acre waterway located within Lakeland Village Park, will measure at 1,000 feet across at its widest point - larger than any existing lake in Bridgeland. A canoe launch, birding tower and space to canoe or kayak three miles from end-to-end make it one of most unique features in the community thus far.\r\n\r\nBridgeland won the 2013 “Master Planned Development of the Year” award from the Greater Houston Builders Association (GHBA), just one of the more than 100 accolades the community has received. For more information on Bridgeland, visit <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/">www.bridgeland.com</a>, Facebook or Twitter.', 'Perry Homes Opens New Model in Hidden Creek', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'perry-homes-opens-new-model-in-hidden-creek', '', '', '2015-09-24 19:03:10', '2015-09-24 19:03:10', '', 0, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/?p=460', 0, 'post', '', 0),
