(464, 1, '2014-09-30 19:04:52', '2014-09-30 19:04:52', 'Taylor Morrison has announced the beginning of pre-sales for its new Legacy Series collection in one of Houston’s most anticipated communities, Bridgeland.\r\n\r\nPriced from the high $400,000s, the Legacy Series is comprised of six floor plans that have been tested throughout the Houston area and provide living spaces that fit today’s homebuyer, said Jim Ellison, vice president of sales and marketing for Taylor Morrison’s Houston division.<span class="caption none media-image alignright size-medium wp-image-2418"><a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/files/taylormorrisonki1541310a-300x1994jpg"><img class="alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/Taylor_Morrison_ki_1541310a-300x199_4.jpg?itok=vP-oWnvR" alt="Taylor_Morrison_ki_1541310a" width="220" height="146" /></a></span>\r\n\r\n“They’re homes that offer plenty of options to accommodate the needs and desires of our homebuyers,” Ellison said. “Being able to offer them at Bridgeland pairs them with a community that is truly a destination in northwest Houston.”\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nTaylor Morrison’s Bridgeland floor plans include both single and two-story designs, with up to four bedrooms and 3.5 baths. Home options range from the Altessa, a 3,265-square-foot single-story plan with four bedrooms to the Florence, with 4,010 square feet, four bedrooms and two floors of living space.\r\n\r\nOptions at Bridgeland include additional bedrooms, media rooms, game rooms, secondary master suites and more.\r\n\r\nThe 11,400-acre, master-planned Bridgeland offers homebuyers amenities that aren’t normally found in northwest Houston, including more than 3,000 acres of dedicated open space, natural lakes and wildlife that help make Bridgeland a sustainable community. The community also boasts more than 60 miles of planned walking trails, village and activity centers as well as an on-site elementary school.\r\n\r\n“It’s a truly special community,” Ellison said. “When everything is completed, there will be more than 900 acres of lakes and waterways at Bridgeland, plenty of outdoor activities as well as the resort-style amenities Houston homebuyers crave.”\r\n\r\nFor more information about pre-sales at Bridgeland, please contact Ashelea Pinzon at houstononline(AT)taylormorrison.com or (281) 780-4652.', 'Taylor Morrison Annouces Pre-Sales in Bridgeland', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'taylor-morrison-annouces-pre-sales-in-bridgeland', '', '', '2015-09-24 19:05:22', '2015-09-24 19:05:22', '', 0, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/?p=464', 0, 'post', '', 0),
