(472, 1, '2014-07-31 19:14:56', '2014-07-31 19:14:56', 'Two well-respected builders, David Weekley and J. Kyle, will soon begin selling homes in the newest sections of Lakeland Heights. Starting in the $250s, these homes will be set on 50’ and 60’ foot lots and range in square footage.<span class="caption none media-image alignright size-medium wp-image-2376"><a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/files/bridgeland-8754wk3-300x1964jpg"><img class="alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/bridgeland-8754_wk3-300x196_4.jpg?itok=ESxqxEUO" alt="Lakeland Heights" width="220" height="144" /></a></span>\r\n\r\nAs Bridgeland’s traditional neighborhood design (TND) development, Lakeland Heights was created to have the aesthetic appeal and accessibility of classic Houston neighborhoods like The Heights and West University, but with the updated amenities of a new community. Consequently, homes in Lakeland Heights blend Craftsmen, English Tudor, Classical and French styles and are walking distance from parks, recreational facilities and schools. Eventually, residents will also be able to easily access shops and restaurants in Lakeland Village Center, a commercial anchor for the 350-home community.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nFestival Park, a hub of the community, contains a covered pavilion for outdoor concerts, plays and performances. The pavilion also houses picnic tables, restrooms and a fireplace with a seating area. Another highlight is Lakeland Heights'' half-mile waterway, which features a landmark bridge, trails, creatively landscaped park space and seating areas\r\n\r\nFor more information on Lakeland Heights, visit <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/lakeland-heights">http://www.bridgeland.com/lakeland-heights</a>.', 'David Weekley and J. Kyle Begin Selling Homes in Newest Sections of Lakeland Heights', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'david-weekley-and-j-kyle-begin-selling-homes-in-newest-sections-of-lakeland-heights', '', '', '2015-09-24 19:15:26', '2015-09-24 19:15:26', '', 0, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/?p=472', 0, 'post', '', 0);
