(478, 1, '2014-07-01 19:17:44', '2014-07-01 19:17:44', 'The Farmers Market at Bridgeland will be buzzing with activity Sunday, July 13 from 12:30-3:30 p.m. with an observation bee hive and more than 35 local vendors.<span class="caption none media-image size-medium wp-image-2360 alignright"><a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/files/399230101522191847560151537303358n-244x3004jpg"><img class="alignright" src="http://www.bridgeland.com/sites/default/files/styles/medium/public/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/399230_10152219184756015_1537303358_n-244x300_4.jpg?itok=qOyy17NE" alt="399230_10152219184756015_1537303358_n" width="179" height="220" /></a></span>\r\n\r\nA long-time merchant at the market, PEAS Farm, will lead the special exhibit, which will teach attendees about the various benefits of raw, local honey while offering a glimpse into a working beehive.\r\n\r\n“Most people don’t realize how vitally important honeybees and pollination are to the world,” said Patricia d’Agrella, a beekeeper at PEAS Farm with 19 years of experience. “By seeing a fully-functioning hive in action during the observation, people will learn about why bees are so important to the environment, as well as how consuming honey helps with allergies, energy levels and general wellbeing.”\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\nAlongside local honey, shoppers will find an abundance of seasonal produce, free-range eggs, floral-infused vinegars, grass-fed beef, homemade jellies and fresh pastas. Other specialty vendors will offer goods like all-natural cleaning supplies and Texas lavender beauty products.\r\n\r\nHeld on the second Sunday of every month near Bridgeland’s Lakeland Activity Center, 16902 Bridgeland Landing, The Farmers Market at Bridgeland unites community farmers, growers and producers with area residents. To see a full list of this month’s participating vendors, visit <a href="http://www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org/">www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org.</a>\r\n\r\nLearn more about Bridgeland, a wholly-owned subsidiary of <a href="http://www.howardhughes.com/">The Howard Hughes Corporation</a> and part of <a href="http://www.thewoodlands.com/">The Woodlands Development Company</a>, at <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/">www.bridgeland.com</a> or <a href="http://www.facebook.com/BridgelandCommunity">www.facebook.com/BridgelandCommunity</a>.', 'The Farmers Market at Bridgeland to Feature Observation Bee Hive July 13', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-farmers-market-at-bridgeland-to-feature-observation-bee-hive-july-13', '', '', '2015-09-24 19:18:23', '2015-09-24 19:18:23', '', 0, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/?p=478', 0, 'post', '', 0),
