dgeland is held on the second Sunday of each month near Bridgeland’s Lakeland Activity Center, 16902 Bridgeland Landing. To see a full list of participating vendors, visit<a href="file:///C:/Users/audrey.roeder/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Temporary%20Internet%20Files/Content.Outlook/0CHEWO1Q/www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org">www.farmersmarketatbridgeland.org</a>.  Learn more about Bridgeland, a wholly owned subsidiary of <a href="http://www.howardhughes.com/">The Howard Hughes Corporation</a> and part of <a href="http://www.thewoodlands.com/">The Woodlands Development Company</a>, at <a href="http://www.bridgeland.com/">www.bridgeland.com</a>.', 'The Farmers Market at Bridgeland Springs to Life March 9', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '502-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-09-24 20:08:59', '2015-09-24 20:08:59', '', 502, 'http://bridgeland.jmmcdigitalhosting.com/502-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
